WEBVTT

00:08.270 --> 00:10.100
My name  is Melinda Gordon

00:12.340 --> 00:17.000
I just got married,just move to a small town,just open *** shoop

00:17.200 --> 00:20.030
And might be just like you

00:20.050 --> 00:24.460
Except from the time that I was a little girl,I knew that I could talk to the dead.

00:25.100 --> 00:26.170
It's all right,honey.

00:26.420 --> 00:28.590
"Earthbound spirits" my grandmother call them.

00:28.980 --> 00:34.540
They stay here because they have unfinished business with the living,and they come to me for help.

00:35.400 --> 00:38.940
To tell you my story,I have to tell you theirs.

